{"tid":876421,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"(都算今日新聞) 騰訊控股嶄露曙光,股東可以自我安慰","createTime":"2018-10-25T15:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T00:56:06.000Z","uid":45440,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"06b2dfa49c96bd67543fc27df630c273761f53b7","tid":876421,"uid":45440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T15:06:58.000Z","msg":"轉貼自[url]<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/stocks/realtime/quote_news_detail.php?newsid=ETN281025511&amp;page=1&amp;section=related&amp;code=700\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fwww%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Frealtime%2Fquote_news_detail.php%3Fnewsid%3DETN281025511%26page%3D1%26section%3Drelated%26code%3D700&d=eMvUS6xmk1IgPRkUV4eKmMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=ad42c25b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/stocks/realtime/quote_news_detail.php?newsid=ETN281025511&amp;page=1&amp;section=related&amp;code=700</a>　<br />\n[/url]<br />\n內地手遊行業嶄露曙光，有統計顯示內地手遊收入的按季增速創近６季最快，騰訊<br />\n（００７００）旗下的《我叫ＭＴ４》，上架僅兩個多月即錄得１５億營收，盡顯「黑馬」姿態<br />\n。<br />\n　　根據遊戲研究機構「伽馬數據」的統計，內地第三季移動遊戲市場的實際銷售收入升至<br />\n３５６﹒１億元（人民幣．下同），按季升９﹒７％，創自２０１７年第二季以來最快增速；按<br />\n年增１６﹒６％，增幅連續兩季擴大。伽馬數據分析，撇除資本開支等因素，手機遊戲產品的增<br />\n長源於市場推動力，原創動漫或文學內容改編的遊戲更是大放異彩，佔據季入新遊戲近４０％的<br />\n收入。<br />\n　　騰訊開發的《王者榮耀》夾５０億元季度流水（營收），蟬聯上季最賺錢手遊。值得留意是<br />\n，由騰訊代理的《我叫ＭＴ４》面世僅兩個多月，季度流水已飇至１５億元，躋身季內新遊戲收<br />\n入榜冠軍，賺錢能力媲美《王者榮耀》及「食雞」遊戲《堡壘之夜海外版》。<br />\n《香港經濟日報》"},{"pid":"36721d454a1d1ddb6c0b6f77197ba5ba332f9b36","tid":876421,"uid":36238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T15:09:26.000Z","msg":"重返400了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fe9362639602de014a6ddddb761efc6b6df15cc","tid":876421,"uid":106426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T15:11:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fbc31e943adb06c41eb2f808799b9c58d7273347","tid":876421,"uid":45440,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T15:11:2